OL,3,CGovernment urged to intervene as pubs
OL,4,Cstruggle with rising costs and tax
OL,5,Crates
OL,7,FThe British Beer and Pub Association
OL,8,Fis calling on the government for more
OL,9,Fsupport for pubs in the capital that
OL,10,Fare struggling with rising costs and
OL,11,Fhigh tax rates
OL,13,FA survey by the BBPA found 59% of
OL,14,FLondoners think business rates for
OL,15,Fpubs are unfair.
OL,17,FIt comes despite data from the Office
OL,18,Ffor National Statistics suggesting
OL,19,FLondon saw a net loss of just 10 pubs
OL,20,Fbetween 2023 and 2024.
