OL,4,Cstruggle with rising costs and tax
OL,5,Crates
OL,7,FThe government says its protecting and
OL,8,Fextending business rates relief.
OL,10,FIn a statement the Treasury added: "We
OL,11,Fknow the vital importance of pubs to
OL,12,Flocal communities and the wider
OL,13,Feconomy, which is why we are
OL,14,Fprotecting pavement pints and al
OL,15,Ffresco dining, have cut alcohol duty
OL,16,Fon draught pints in the pub, and are
OL,17,Fprotecting and extending business
OL,18,Frates relief which would have ended
OL,19,Fwithout this government's action.
