OL,4,Cstruggle with rising costs and tax
OL,5,Crates
OL,7,FKate Davidson, Publican of The Old Ivy
OL,8,FHouse in Clerkenwell said: "We knew it
OL,9,Fwould be tough, but it's become
OL,10,Frelentless.
OL,12,F"We're growing, but the profits don't
OL,13,Freflect that proportionally.
OL,15,F"The pub isn't just about pints; it's
OL,16,Fabout lonely people finding
OL,17,Fconnection, students bonding with
OL,18,Fretirees, and parents feeling welcome.
OL,19,FThat's the value the current rates
OL,20,Fsystem completely ignores."
